{"type": "article", "id": 17838, "title": "带虚拟实境装置的手机壳", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-20T07:10:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134820SmxpAM7Er9vRiYyJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个手机壳，但在壳子上折叠安装了一个虚拟实境装置，翻转到手机屏幕前就可以看 VR 视频了。此外，镜片本身也是一个手机支架，简易而方便。来自美国硅谷的团队 Quantum Bakery 开发了这款产品，有黑白两色可选，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/quantumbakery/figment-vr-virtual-reality-in-your-pocket\" target=\"_blank\">目前正在众筹，</a>预计明年上市。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134816lq9QmeBfyipDSFtv.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021348174k8ZNIK5dCWsRj3y.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"342\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50294118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134818c9fjph5oUvFS63Ke.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"453\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134818lyLgtxVfiv086eCI.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"383\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134819Mc9sPCEWXiUwgh7z.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"432\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63529412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134819SbqAhT1jsO2mZJk7.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"434\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}